      <title>巴菲特的2025年财富在亿万富翁的消灭中脱颖而出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/buffett-s-2025-wealth-gains-stand-out-amid-billionaire-wipeout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在世界上最富有的人群中，沃伦·巴菲特（Warren Buffett）是少数几位在唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的关税引发抛售后，今年个人命运已成长的少数人之一，从而从全球股票中删除了数万亿美元的价值。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/buffett-s-2025-wealth-gains-stand-out-amid-billionaire-wipeout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 22:14:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>7分钟2.5万亿美元的股票集会混淆了警惕的投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/the-7-minute-2-5-trillion-stock-rally-confounds-wary-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[谣言只持续了大约七分钟。那时，股票投资者意识到，唐纳德·特朗普总统在90天内停止关税并不是真的，因此停止了疯狂的竞标股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/the-7-minute-2-5-trillion-stock-rally-confounds-wary-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 21:19:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
