    <item>
      <title>自特朗普当选以来，美元树篱的成本飙升至最高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/cost-of-dollar-hedges-soars-to-highest-since-trump-s-election</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贸易商急于购买对美元秋千的保护，将对冲成本推向自去年11月唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）当选以来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/cost-of-dollar-hedges-soars-to-highest-since-trump-s-election</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 16:38:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>“现在世界有所不同”：市场抽搐袭击了华尔街</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/global-market-meltdown-deepens-as-trump-holds-firm-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在华尔街，交易台和公司C苏装的整个跨越，对冲基金经理和债券经销商中，越来越不安的是，很快有一天，唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）可能最终不仅会破坏经济，而且破坏了金融市场的关键部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/global-market-meltdown-deepens-as-trump-holds-firm-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 05:38:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>EM股票擦除2025收益，因为关税燃料17年来最差的一天</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/emerging-asian-currencies-slip-as-risk-off-extends-on-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）的贸易政策的影响继续在周一继续颠覆全球市场，新兴市场资产削弱了这一年的收益。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-07/emerging-asian-currencies-slip-as-risk-off-extends-on-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 07 Apr 2025 04:58:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
